column5: Hey, I'm up early and there are NO Mods up yet....we can all go nuts....  LOL  See what goes on when you over sleep Roy....
Damn....the Billy Bob alarm must of went off on Chris's computer...  LOL
Go back to counting your Cheerios, redneck. I've been here since 3am.
But you know it only takes me a hour to run out of fingers and toes....  I caused a 2 alarm alert this morning....
Keep at it, we'll be red necklace.
Billy Bob we can put you in the corner for a day to think about what you did
Sorry i just have to ........... that was'nt nieve at its best was it . Good morning every one .
Whats the matter Billy Bob, Tundra needed out for a pee and Cindy wouldn't get up with her or are you just trying to figure out your picks for the football pool for today
I told  ya to put tinfoil under your hat Bob.Its the only way they cant read your mind. You better put 2 layers  Morning
BINGO Cliff on the Tundra up early thing....  And I'm going to kick your Canadian   today with my football picks...you're going down old timer....
In your case it is a very short read, Paul.
Do the animals at the zoo behave the same when no one is watching?
The Tinfoil only works if you wear one of these on top Come ON PAUL you know this stuff
Ya, but didn`t THEY say not to tell the general public about it  This could cause BLEEN, throughout the population.
I wrap my nuts in bacon when this happens...  my chestnuts, for roasting that is...
Geeze, We coulda had dancin' mods and I missed it!!!!!!
